        <abstract>
            <p>He has added carbolic acid to the seed germination experiments and sends more results on the effect of formic acid. Formic acid inhibits mildew on dough but not on seeds.</p>
            <p>Mildew never grows in ants’ nests.</p> 
<p>Sends an account, from the <hi rend="italic">Mishnah</hi>, of grain stored by ants.</p> 
        </abstract>
